2480:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2481:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \brief
2482:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  The function discharge available external capacitors.
2483:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2484:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** * \details
2485:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  The function discharge available external capacitors by connection them
2486:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  to GND using STRONG GPIO drive mode. Additionaly, the function disconnects
2487:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  the capacitors from analog mux buses if connected.
2488:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  Note: the function does not restore the connection to analog mux busses
2489:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *  and supposes that all the capacitors belong to a single device port.
2490:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *
2491:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_Sensing.c **** *******************************************************************************/
